com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx

Interface ParametersMotion

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParametersMotionImpl

    public interface ParametersMotion
    A representation of the model object 'Parameters Motion'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Current Position
    • Empty
    • Operation
    • Operation Number
    • Operation Type

    See Also:
    EsxPackage.getParametersMotion()
